Class VectorListIteratorAdapter

java.lang.Object
myAdapter.VectorIteratorAdapter
myAdapter.VectorListIteratorAdapter
All Implemented Interfaces:
HIterator, HListIterator
public class VectorListIteratorAdapter
extends VectorIteratorAdapter
implements HListIterator
An iterator which iterates a java.util.Vector and implements the HListIterator interface which extends the HIterator interface.

    • VectorListIteratorAdapter

      public VectorListIteratorAdapter​(java.util.Vector v)
      The iterator iterates a java.util.Vector, so when creating the iterator, a java.util.Vector is passed as argument. The iterator iterates the java.util.Vector from the beginning.
      Parameters:
      v - java.util.Vector which the iterator iterates.

    • VectorListIteratorAdapter

      public VectorListIteratorAdapter​(java.util.Vector v, int initialIndex)
      The iterator iterates a java.util.Vector, so when creating the iterator, a java.util.Vector is passed as argument. The iterator iterates the java.util.Vector from the initial index passed by argument.
      Parameters:
      v - java.util.Vector which the iterator iterates.
      initialIndex - The index (inclusively) from which the java.util.Vector is iterated.
